{
  "rationale": "To ensure safe and efficient arena coverage, we introduce a 'scan' helper state for systematic exploration after obstacle encounters. All uncontrollable events are handled in every state. Forward and random walk are only allowed in clear paths. Rotations are used to navigate around obstacles, and a full rotation is used to reorient after being blocked. The scan state prevents oscillations and encourages coverage.",
