  "coverage_strategy": [
    "Favor move_forward or random_walk only when path is clear.",
    "Rotate away from obstacles, choosing direction based on sensor input.",
    "Use 'scan' state (with full_rotate or small rotations) to systematically search for new directions after being blocked.",
    "Avoid repeated oscillations by not immediately reversing rotation after obstacle detection.",
    "Prioritize systematic coverage by alternating between forward movement and scanning when blocked."
